        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1795",
        "content": "Next there was the market place, with all its clamorous joys; and when a runaway calf came down the street like a cannon ball, Harold felt that he had not lived in vain.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
