        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1795",
        "content": "Then Harold, with the unnatural courage born of desperation, flung himself on the step, and climbing into the cart, fell in the straw at the bottom of it, sobbing out that he wanted to go back, go back!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
